column2: Births where the the usual residence of mother were not stated or were to non residents of England and Wales have been excluded from these figures. Of the 370,974 baby boys in the 2011 dataset, 98 were excluded for these reasons.
Births where the name was not stated have also been excluded from these figures, 13 baby boys have been excluded from the 2011 dataset for this reason.
